name: Odading Mang Oleh The Game
description:
ODADING MANG OLEH THE GAME BY ADITYA NUR HUDA

Mang Oleh is a viral food vendor in indonesia that sell Odading and Cakue. Odading is a fried bread from Bandung in the form of a bubble box. Odading Mang Oleh the game is a game themed by Mang Oleh, who is eating objects that fall from the sky. You have to eat all the food that falls from the sky and don't catch the coronavirus and shark attacks. Odading Mang Oleh, rasanya ajib banget..!

Special thanks to Rizky Ayuba for make this great song and "Channel Kita"
